Revision history for RPi-BMP180

3.1802 UNREL
    - Added TECHNICAL INFORMATION POD (DEVICE SPECIFICS, REGISTER MAP, ON THE
      WIRE, DATASHEET): chip capabilities, wiring, the full register map, and
      the I2C frames wiringPi's devLib bmp180.c produces, verified against
      the Bosch BST-BMP180-DS000-09 datasheet
    - Fixed POD typos: SYNOPSIS constructor call was RPi::BMP180($base),
      missing the ->new; temp() misspelled Fahrenheit and Celsius
    - Bundled the datasheet as docs/datasheet/BMP180.pdf and repointed the
      DATASHEET POD section at it instead of the web URL
    - Dropped the vestigial LIBS => ['-lwiringPi', '-lwiringPiDev'] from
      Makefile.PL; this dist is pure Perl (no XS), so nothing links those
      libraries - the entry was inert leftover from a former XS incarnation
    - _pin_base() now croaks (with the caller's location) instead of die on a
      non-integer or unset pin base
    - Added t/05-unit.t: HW-free coverage of _pin_base() validation (non-integer
      and unset croaks, valid set/get) and new() croaking without a pin base

3.1801    2026-06-12
        - added Github info to Makefile.PL
        - changed from RPi::WiringPi::Const to RPi::Const
        - Removed leftover use of removed RPi::WiringPi::Constant (no
          constants are used in this module)
        - Bump prereq of WiringPi::API to 3.1801
        - Bump prereq of RPi::Const to 1.05

2.3604  2017-06-28
        - bump prereq of WiringPi::API to 2.3612
        - bump prereq of RPi::WiringPi::Constant to 1.00

2.3603  2017-03-13
        - changed version numbering from 2.36.x to 2.360x
        - changed prereq vers as well

2.36.2  2017-02-02
        - fix typo in prereq ver of WiringPi::API, 2.36.6 -> 2.36.4

2.36.1  2017-02-02
        - initial standalone version harvested from RPi::WiringPi
